    • version

    • customs

      public final java.util.List<CustomNode>[] customs
      An array of lists of CustomNodes that this module has.

      Since modules can contain custom sections between any two defined sections, there is a space in this array for a list of custom nodes after each defined section:

      customs[SECTION_CUSTOM] is visited before any of the other sections, and customs[SECTION_XXX] is visited after the section SECTION_XXX, where SECTION_XXX is one of the SECTION_XXX constants in Opcodes.

    • accept

      public void accept​(ModuleVisitor mv)
      Make the given ModuleVisitor visit the header and all the sections of this node.

      The order in which custom sections are visited is as described on the customs field.

      Parameters:
      mv - The visitor to visit.

    • getCustoms

      @NotNull public @NotNull java.util.List<CustomNode> getCustoms​(byte section)

      Parameters:

      Returns:
